
# MythBlazor

An experimental MythTV frontend created with Microsoft Blazor.


## Building

Clone the project

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/BobEntwhistle/MythBlazor.git
```

Open and Build in Visual Studio 2026+



## Generating New API Clients

Edit `~/WsdlToOpenApi.Runner/wsdls.json`

Change IP addresses/ports to match the backend you are querying for WSDL definitions.
```bash
[
  "http://192.168.0.100:6544/Video/wsdl?raw=1",
  "http://192.168.0.100:6544/Dvr/wsdl?raw=1",
  "http://192.168.0.100:6544/Guide/wsdl?raw=1",
  "http://192.168.0.100:6544/Content/wsdl?raw=1"
]
```
## Running the Frontend

Edit `~/MythBlazor/wwwroot/appsettings.json`

Change IP address/port to match the backend you are querying for MythTV Services.
```json
"APIinfo": {
  "ApiUrl": "http://192.168.0.100:6544"
}
```
Run the MythBlazor project.